          <p>Placements at Amrita have always been excellent. Students who are eligible and opted for placements have
            more than one job offer, on an average. Exercising their dream option, some of them have up to three job
            offers by the end of their course.</p>

          <p>For the year 2018-19, a total of 306 eligible students were placed at Amrita School of Business (ASB) at
            salaries that have shown significant growth over the previous years. The placements have provided them
            high-quality, diverse and professional opportunities. For the year 2019-20, as on July 2020, a total of 271
            eligible students are placed and the process is still going on.</p>
            <h3>Highlights</h3>

